item.title: Developing a Project
item.description: Creating a HarkerDev project requires more than simply writing the code. This tutorial summarizes the steps to fully creating a official, Harker-recognized HarkerDev project. Phase 1: Authorization Step 1: Define Project Function Once the Administration approves the idea of the project, the function of the project must be clearly defined. The idea of a project is different from its defined function. For example, the function of the Course Planner project was streamlining the course planning process.
